---
import PageShell from '../../../../components/PageShell.astro';
import CTABox from '../../../../components/CTABox.astro';
import ComparisonTable from '../../../../components/ComparisonTable.astro';

const tocItems = [
  { id: 'overview', text: 'SafetyWing in Germany', level: 2 },
  { id: 'plans-and-pricing', text: 'Plans and Pricing', level: 2 },
  { id: 'germany-limitations', text: 'Important Limitations', level: 2 },
  { id: 'who-its-for', text: 'Who Should Choose SafetyWing', level: 2 },
];

const relatedLinks = [
  { title: 'Health Insurance in Germany', href: '/countries/germany/insurance' },
  { title: 'SafetyWing Review', href: '/providers/safetywing' },
  { title: 'SafetyWing vs Cigna', href: '/compare/safetywing-vs-cigna-global' },
];

const planColumns = [
  { key: 'plan', header: 'Plan' },
  { key: 'coverage', header: 'Coverage' },
  { key: 'germanyPrice', header: 'Germany Price' },
];

const planRows = [
  { plan: 'Nomad Insurance', coverage: 'Travel medical', germanyPrice: '€45/mo' },
  { plan: 'Remote Health', coverage: 'Comprehensive health', germanyPrice: '€190-260/mo' },
];
---

<PageShell
  title="SafetyWing Insurance in Germany"
  description="Guide to using SafetyWing in Germany. Limitations, visa compliance issues, and when it works."
  headline="SafetyWing Insurance in Germany"
  subheadline="SafetyWing for digital nomads in Germany—understand the serious limitations before relying on it."
  heroBackgroundImage="/images/countries/germany-hero-bg.png"
  tocItems={tocItems}
  relatedLinks={relatedLinks}
  ctaButtonText="Get SafetyWing"
  ctaButtonHref="/providers/safetywing"
>
  <h2 id="overview">SafetyWing in Germany</h2>
  <p>
    SafetyWing is popular with digital nomads for its affordable pricing, but Germany's strict insurance requirements make it problematic for long-term stays. Germany mandates comprehensive health insurance—SafetyWing's Nomad Insurance likely doesn't qualify.
  </p>

  <div class="bg-red-50 border border-red-200 rounded-lg p-6 my-6">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-red-900 mb-2">Critical Warning for Germany</h3>
    <p class="text-red-800">
      Germany legally requires all residents to have GKV or PKV-equivalent insurance. SafetyWing Nomad Insurance is travel medical insurance and almost certainly does not meet German legal requirements. Using only SafetyWing for residency in Germany may result in legal issues and back-payment of premiums.
    </p>
  </div>

  <CTABox
    title="Need Germany-Compliant Coverage?"
    description="Consider comprehensive options that meet German requirements."
    buttonText="Compare Compliant Plans"
    buttonHref="/best/expat-health-insurance"
    variant="highlight"
  />

  <h2 id="plans-and-pricing">Plans and Pricing</h2>

  <div class="my-8 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
    <ComparisonTable columns={planColumns} rows={planRows} />
  </div>

  <h3>Nomad Insurance vs Remote Health</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Nomad Insurance (~€45/mo):</strong> Travel medical—NOT sufficient for German residency</li>
    <li><strong>Remote Health (~€190-260/mo):</strong> Comprehensive—may work for initial periods, verify compliance</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="germany-limitations">Important Limitations in Germany</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Legal compliance:</strong> Nomad Insurance doesn't meet German mandatory insurance laws</li>
    <li><strong>Visa applications:</strong> May not be accepted for German visa applications</li>
    <li><strong>Back-payments:</strong> If you're later found non-compliant, you may owe GKV premiums retroactively</li>
    <li><strong>Limited coverage:</strong> Lower limits than German-compliant plans</li>
    <li><strong>No long-term solution:</strong> Germany requires enrollment in GKV or PKV</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>When SafetyWing Might Work</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Very short tourist stays (under 90 days)</li>
    <li>Supplementary coverage alongside GKV</li>
    <li>As travel insurance for trips outside Germany</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="who-its-for">Who Should Choose SafetyWing in Germany</h2>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
    <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-green-900 mb-3">Potentially OK</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-green-800">
        <li>Short tourist visits (under 90 days)</li>
        <li>Supplementary travel coverage</li>
        <li>Those with GKV wanting travel insurance</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-red-50 border border-red-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-red-900 mb-3">Not Recommended</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-red-800">
        <li>Anyone seeking German residency</li>
        <li>Freelancer visa applicants</li>
        <li>Long-term stays in Germany</li>
        <li>Those without other compliant coverage</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <CTABox
    title="Need Proper Germany Coverage?"
    description="Get insurance that actually meets German legal requirements."
    buttonText="See Compliant Plans"
    buttonHref="/countries/germany/insurance"
    variant="highlight"
  />

  <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6 mt-8">
    <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">
      <strong>Disclaimer:</strong> German insurance law is strict. Verify all coverage with German authorities and consider consulting an insurance advisor before relying on any international insurance for German residency.
    </p>
  </div>
</PageShell>
